# UI/UX 디자인 규칙

## 색상 팔레트 (고정)

```css
/* Primary - 메인 브랜드 색상 */
--primary: #111827;        /* bg-primary, text-primary */

/* Secondary - 강조/액션 색상 */
--secondary: #FFD400;      /* bg-secondary, bg-[#FFD400] */
--secondary-hover: #FFC400;

/* 상태 색상 */
--success: #22C55E;        /* green-500 */
--warning: #F59E0B;        /* yellow-500, orange-500 */
--error: #EF4444;          /* red-500 */
--info: #40C1C7;           /* cyan */

/* 배경 색상 */
--bg-page: #F8F9FA;
--bg-card: #FFFFFF;
--bg-section: #F3F6F9;
--bg-input: #F9FAFB;       /* gray-50 */

/* 테두리 */
--border-light: #F3F4F6;   /* gray-100 */
--border-medium: #E5E7EB;  /* gray-200 */
```

---

## 컴포넌트 스타일 규칙

### 카드
```tsx
// 대시보드 카드
<div className="bg-white rounded-[32px] p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">

// 위젯 카드
<div className="bg-white rounded-[40px] p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">

// 섹션 카드
<div className="bg-surface-light rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6">
```

### 버튼
```tsx
// Primary 버튼 (노란색)
<button className="px-10 py-3.5 rounded-2xl bg-[#FFD400] text-gray-900 
  font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest 
  hover:bg-[#FFC400] active:scale-95 shadow-xl shadow-yellow-200/50">

// Secondary 버튼 (테두리)
<button className="px-6 py-3 rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-100 bg-white 
  text-gray-500 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest 
  hover:bg-gray-50 hover:border-gray-200 active:scale-95">

// Success 버튼 (완료)
<button className="bg-green-500 text-white shadow-green-200">

// Disabled 버튼
<button className="bg-gray-200 text-gray-400 cursor-not-allowed shadow-none" disabled>
```

### 입력 필드
```tsx
<div className="relative rounded-md shadow-sm">
  <div className="pointer-events-none absolute inset-y-0 left-0 flex items-center pl-3">
    <span className="material-icons-round text-gray-400 text-xl">phone</span>
  </div>
  <input
    className="block w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 pl-10 
      focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary sm:text-sm py-3"
    type="text"
  />
</div>
```

